This is TIC-TAC-TOE API
=======================

This API is used to play tic-tac-toe game between HUMAN and COMPUTER.
The HUMAN player plays with "x" symbol and sends this new moves through an API request: "curl APP_URL?board=+xxo++o++"
The COMPUTER player plays with "o" symbol and responds to the API request with a new board containing this new move as well.

The main controller containing all necessary functions of the game can be found in "app/com/pbaraka/controllers/Game.java"


Demo: https://salty-shelf-18899.herokuapp.com/play?board=++x++++++

Developed by Patient Baraka
